      <section id="id6927946">
        <title>To write lists with headings [LO 4.1.2]</title>
        <para id="id2703298">SHOPPING CENTRE</para>
        <para id="id5965334">a) You are going to the shopping centre. You have a shopping list with everything you must buy. You will have to go to many different shops. List your items under different shop names according to where you will buy them.</para>
