        <para id="id6945153">d) Divide into groups of four. Choose characters from the following list: Parent, shopkeeper, son, daughter, and another customer. Plan a role-play with dialogue. Ensure that each character has at least four sentences to say. Practise your play until you know it well. Present it to the class.</para>
